        <h3>4.1 THIRD PARTIES THAT PROVIDE CONTENT OR FUNCTIONALITY ON OUR SERVICES</h3>
        <p>We partner with certain third parties to collect, analyze, and use some of the Personal Information described in this Policy. For example:</p>
        <ul>
        <li>
        <p>Third-parties that provide features and functionality on the Services by means of plug-ins. Even if you do not click on or interact with social networking services or other plug-ins, they collect information about you, such as your IP address and the pages that you view.</p>
        </li>
